14/*
15 Conditions:
16 outSize <= FullOutputSize,
17 where FullOutputSize is full size of output stream of x86_2 filter.
18
19 If buf0 overlaps outBuf, there are two required conditions:
20 1) (buf0 >= outBuf)
21 2) (buf0 + size0 >= outBuf + FullOutputSize).
22
23 Returns:
24 SZ_OK
25 SZ_ERROR_DATA - Data error
26 */
27
28int Bcj2_Decode(const Byte *buf0, SizeT size0, const Byte *buf1, SizeT size1, const Byte *buf2, SizeT size2, const Byte *buf3, SizeT size3,
29 Byte *outBuf, SizeT outSize);
